Turkey Removes Prosecutors in Corruption Probe, Hurriyet Says

-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 
2011-08-27T13:39:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-27/turkey-removes-prosecutors-in-corruption-probe-hurriyet-says.html
Turkey ’s board of prosecutors and
judges removed three prosecutors directing the probe into a
financial corruption scandal involving the former head of the
state broadcasting watchdog,  Hurriyet  said.  The three prosecutors were removed after complaints to the
board from the defendants’ lawyers, the Istanbul-based paper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
